\v 10 Ngingowesithandwa sami\x + 2.16. 6.3.\x*, lesifiso saso singakimi\x + Gen. 3.16. Gen. 4.7. Hlab. 45.11.\x*.
\v 11 Woza, sithandwa sami, kasiphumele egangeni, silale ebusuku emizaneni;
\v 12 kasivuke ngovivi siye ezivinini, sibone ukuthi amavini asehluma\x + 6.11.\x*, ekhupha impoko\x + 2.13.\x*, \add lokuthi\add* \w amapomegranati\w** akhahlele yini. Lapho ngizakunika uthando lwami\x + 6.11.\x*.
\v 13 \w Amamandrake\w** akhupha iphunga elimnandi\x + Gen. 30.14.\x*, langasemasangweni ethu\x + 2.17.\x* kukhona zonke inhlobo zezithelo ezimnandi kakhulu\x + 4.13.\x*, ezintsha lezindala\x + Mat. 13.52.\x*, \add e\add*ngizibekele wena, sithandwa sami\x + Jobe 23.12.\x*.
